{"tid":1487118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信美國國會議員支持《香港人權及民主法案2019》","createTime":"2019-08-19T06:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T17:23:57.000Z","uid":309895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e6b2e02f0f0d58933980ce33579194264b7a4de8","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次上連登出POST,寫得唔好請見諒。我想請大家一人一信寫比美國國會議員，要求支持 《香港人權及民主法案2019》Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act of 2019，比美國國會聽到香港人對反送中、維持司法獨立的訴求。<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我覺得呢個係最有效既方法令政府回應香港人訴求,下面有講點解。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n填下個人資料就得,裡面已經有封寫好既信(有誠意啲既就自己改下啦),填一次直接寄比參議員同眾議員。唔係住喺美國都唔緊要(地址可以揀唔係美國),最緊要比美國國會知道好多香港人好支持呢個法案,叫埋親朋戚友寫。<br />\n<br />\n大家為呢場運動付出咁多,叫你寫多封EMAIL都唔過份啫? 同埋唔該同我推爆佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019?source=direct_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Factionnetwork.org%2Fletters%2Fco-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019%3Fsource%3Ddirect_link&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=c6dd04ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019?source=direct_link</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">點解有用?</span></span></strong><br />\n- 兩個多月來，香港和北京政府對百萬市民上街示威和平示威和更激烈抗爭行動仍然不痛不癢，皆因<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">當權者及權貴在香港核心利益仍然冇受嚴重受影響，中國繼續藉著香港特殊地位繞過美國關稅及高科技出口禁運從中得益</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n- 根據中國商務部數據，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港佔全中國外商直接投資74% ，501億美元（2019年1-6月）</span></strong>，香港對內地經濟及公司融資持續擔當關鍵角色。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簡單講句,冇香港,大陸公司就吸納唔到外資。</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mofcom.gov.cn/&hellip;/to&hellip;/v/201907/20190702885883.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mofcom.gov.cn%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fto%E2%80%A6%2Fv%2F201907%2F20190702885883.shtml&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=82e2fdfd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mofcom.gov.cn/&hellip;/to&hellip;/v/201907/20190702885883.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouvqvYf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouvqvYf.jpg&h=efd54279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[Source: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kengopage/posts/2494038077324569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkengopage%2Fposts%2F2494038077324569&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=bf326024\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kengopage/posts/2494038077324569</a>]<br />\n<br />\n- 呢條草案會每年監察香港人權法治情況，決定係咪延續《香港關係法1992》美國賦予香港特殊優惠同關稅地位(侵侵對大陸徵既關稅香港係唔使比架)。簡單啲講，<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">北京令香港冇法治同自由，美國就取消對香港優惠，變成大陸一個普通城市，大陸企業就好難再吸納外資。大陸經濟本身已經放緩，再加上經濟制裁，經濟衰退唔係冇可能，呢點應該會令北京投鼠忌器。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n- 呢條草案會定期檢討香港有冇落實美國出口法規，唔比大陸從香港將禁運中國既高科技產品轉口內地(大陸想發展大灣區做科技港都係靠由香港入口高科技)<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>以上呢兩點觸及北京在香港核心利益，直接有效地增加北京不回應香港人訴求的成本</strong></span></span>。令北京當局明白美國給予香港特殊關係是基於香港仍然維持自由、司法獨立和法治的大前提。<br />\n<br />\n- 凍結侵犯香港人人身自由既人既美國資產同禁止佢地入境, 呢點既作用好明顯唔多講啦<br />\n<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢條法案過到，分分鐘係香港既護身符，派老解落黎既機會更加低。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我呢度講既野以前已經有人講過，但係我唔明點解冇乜人提起同參與，白宮聯署十萬個名一日就搞掂，點解到而家先寄得果2700封EMAIL? 我真係覺得呢件事好有用，唔該大家幫下手啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AWhwrmb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAWhwrmb.jpg&h=c9e85a60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d1f2c95342b435a84adfa32142af98ee24533f6","tid":1487118,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaQFjHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaQFjHY.jpg&h=817efdb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hvFjHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hvFjHY.jpg&h=2bfb32da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72bed5d00dfee65503c2b8fabc3ce90d56b5f02d","tid":1487118,"uid":309989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"Support 推"},{"pid":"13943c73a5a4df92de6939df0176e9fad7a4859f","tid":1487118,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95a1993b31b4f573613ca9e059aec71b143b2478","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n- 根據中國商務部數據，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港佔全中國外商直接投資74% ，501億美元（2019年1-6月）</span></strong>，香港對內地經濟及公司融資持續擔當關鍵角色。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簡單講句,冇香港,大陸公司就吸納唔到外資。</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mofcom.gov.cn/&hellip;/to&hellip;/v/201907/20190702885883.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mofcom.gov.cn%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fto%E2%80%A6%2Fv%2F201907%2F20190702885883.shtml&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=82e2fdfd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mofcom.gov.cn/&hellip;/to&hellip;/v/201907/20190702885883.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上面中國商務部數據條link唔work，用呢條：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mofcom.gov.cn/article/tongjiziliao/v/201907/20190702885883.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mofcom.gov.cn%2Farticle%2Ftongjiziliao%2Fv%2F201907%2F20190702885883.shtml&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=5bad9a06\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mofcom.gov.cn/article/tongjiziliao/v/201907/20190702885883.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"ddfcc2cbfa649839e1062abd5567d71e32cef40b","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"同樣的觀點和分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/123772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F123772&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=76fa3638\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/123772</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手推下啦，唔該"},{"pid":"a8a58245e2b85991486f69aa3d43f7554a2d257a","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"17e07f1cfdb6b38a986c316d1db349422dce231a","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"68ae0082667ce2a9291d23f1fce8b773fe532a9e","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:25:31.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"707b2cf2bc2a8612ddadb5757d4f546a557e981e","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:25:46.000Z","msg":"八"},{"pid":"060e0dc7f1e9e23caf0f23c0123067f759eaa7e5","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"七"},{"pid":"d538ec924eafbe71caa09a6f56e5ee618a2cb300","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"f237ca4618c3266ecd6f197ac8d924c46b5062fd","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:27:09.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"ba683cb3c1ce219a6f7a2dc0af1f0a635835fd39","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"e26ba910523aa6314c95e28e4ec6bc7496fc9094","tid":1487118,"uid":309895,